  "guide": {
    "title": "Umhlahlandlela wekucopha weSuno",
    "subtitle": "Indlela yekubamba iphimbo nesigingci kutsatsa kutsi utfole imiphumela lemihle kakhulu.",
    "intro": "Suno wenta kahle kakhulu ngetikhombo letihlantekile, letingacaci. Lomhlahlandlela uhlanganisa kulungiselela, emazinga lahlosiwe, kanye neskripthi sekubhala semizuzu lengu-3-5.",
    "sections": {
      "prep": {
        "title": "Kulungiselela",
        "body": "Rekhoda ekamelweni leliphatsiwe noma lelinye lelinetintfo letinyenti letitfobekile (emakhethini, emaragi, timphahla ekhabetheni). Cisha balandzeli nanoma yini lehubhutako. Futfumala livi lakho imizuzu lengu-5 ngaphambi kwekutsi urekhode."
      },
      "levels": {
        "title": "Emazinga: -12 kuya ku -6 dBFS",
        "body": "Hlela ticoco letisemkhatsini we -12 na -6 dBFS emitha. Ngaphansi kwalelo banga, umsindvo wangemuva uyabonakala kakhulu; ngetulu kwayo, ingoti yekusika iyakhuphuka. Sebentisa imitha ekhasini leRekhodi kusetha inzuzo yakho ngaphambi kwekutsi ucale."
      },
      "distance": {
        "title": "Libanga le-mic: 15-30 cm",
        "body": "Hlala 15 kuya ku 30 cm kusuka kumbhobho. Eduze kunaloko ihabisa plosives kanye nemphumela wekusondzelana; khashane ucosha igumbi reverb ngaphezulu kanye umsindo."
      },
      "script": {
