      "warmup_inst": "Khulula ngekuzamula, kukhala kwetindzebe (brrr), kanye nekuhubha lokuthambile cishe umzuzu. Asikho sidzingo sekubhala — kumane nje kuphumula umphimbo wakho ngaphambi kwekuhlabela.",
      "vowels": "Onkamisa labasimeme",
