      "scales": "Tikali letikhuphukako naphansi",
      "scales_inst": "Hlabelela sikali lesilula phezulu bese wehla, ku \"la\" noma \"na\". Akudzingeki kutsi kube ngulokuphelele — umgomo kutsi ubeke imephu yebanga lakho le-vocal.",
